OL,6,FHe becomes the first offender to be
OL,7,Fconvicted as part of wide-ranging
OL,8,Finvestigations into historical child
OL,9,Fsexual abuse in Manchester in the
OL,10,F2000s. Operation Green Jacket is being
OL,11,Fled by Greater Manchester Police's
OL,12,Fdedicated Child Sexual Exploitation
OL,13,FMajor Incident Team.
OL,15,FThe court had begun to hear evidence
OL,16,Fof how Oates, from Stockport and
OL,17,Fnicknamed 'Nails' due to his long
OL,18,Ffingernails, groomed the girls and
OL,19,Fpreyed on their vulnerability.
