OL,9,Fsex work and sell her to other men.
OL,11,FThe victim approached GMP in November
OL,12,F2020 after seeing media coverage of
OL,13,Fother arrests as part of Operation
OL,14,FGreen Jacket.
OL,16,FShe and her friend recorded video
OL,17,Fevidence detailing Oates' abuse. This
OL,18,Fwas played in court earlier this week
OL,19,Fbefore Oates decided to admit his
OL,20,Fcrimes.
