OL,6,FDetective Inspector Eleanor
OL,7,FHumphrey's, senior investigating
OL,8,Fofficer for this case, said: "I am so
OL,9,Fpleased for both women that they have
OL,10,Ftoday finally got some justice all
OL,11,Fthese years after this horrific abuse.
OL,13,F"Christopher Oates is a depraved and
OL,14,Fmanipulative paedophile. The abuse he
OL,15,Fsubjected these two girls to was
OL,16,Fhorrific. He was even prepared to try
OL,17,Fand deny this throughout a trial and
OL,18,Fmake the victims relive it all over
OL,19,Fagain.
