OL,6,F"Firstly, I commend the bravery of the
OL,7,Fvictims and the meticulous dedication
OL,8,Fof the investigation team and support
OL,9,Fservices. Together, long-awaited
OL,10,Fjustice has been secured.
OL,12,F"Operation Green Jacket was set up in
OL,13,F2019 to tackle non-recent child
OL,14,Fexploitation in Manchester in the
OL,15,F2000s. This result is a clear signal
OL,16,Fwe will investigate and we will bring
OL,17,Foffenders to justice.
